Linux:
without RSTCPU: EP0 handling in main loop works
                EP0 handling inside interrupt does not work

with RSTCPU: EP0 handling in main loop works
             EP0 handling inside interrupt works

Windows:
without RSTCPU: EP0 handling in main loop works
                EP0 handling inside interrupt does not work

with RSTCPU: EP0 handling in main loop does not work
             EP0 handling inside interrupt does not work
